chunks.text: Five popcorn in the bankage shop, round it
dead with a cross on the top.
Along came a girl with somebody one day.
The bull of crossland and took it right away.
Four popcorn in the baking shop, Ran dead with the cross on the top
Along came a boy with the money,
One day
Board of cross fanny took it right away
Three puffsland in the baking shop
Rounding dead with the cross on the top
Along came a girl with the money one day
Borda Posterousbanded took it right away
Two across man in the bank in shop
Round in bed with the cross on the top
Along came a boy just a money one day
board across the sun and took it right away
One puffer spun in the vacant shop
Round and fed with the cross on the top
Along came a girl with somebody one day
And brought a hopper study and took it twice away
